{"tid":894482,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[魔獸世界]台服日屠銀部落香港公會<Raid or Laid>現正招生","createTime":"2018-11-08T12:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T13:09:08.000Z","uid":108226,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f59ea2be5c46da0bd697cbcc6170c24258989403","tid":894482,"uid":108226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/Q0oZ40.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FQ0oZ40.gif&h=cfa91acc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tDMTBBx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtDMTBBx.jpg&h=a87c1d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/02/140057_21d765cb25ff90b854ecb4fb1656a7d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2F140057_21d765cb25ff90b854ecb4fb1656a7d9.jpg&h=dd4e5e6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&lt;Raid or Laid&gt;<br />\n係一個日屠銀既100%香港公會<br />\n現活躍人數大既30人+<br />\n我地致力集合各位香港玩家一齊打本吹水交流<br />\n締造一個同聲同氣既公會<br />\n唔理你新手定老手 最緊要成班巴打玩得開心<br />\n要女有女，要棍有棍<br />\n<br />\n公會活動:每星期一，二，四晚上900公會團<br />\n另外會有不定時小號團<br />\n<br />\n公會現時進度: H 8/8, M 3/8<br />\n<br />\n空缺：遠程DPS、補 (其它亦可考慮, DH 滿)<br />\n要求：穩定，裝等３４０＋，兼職亦可另外商議<br />\n<br />\n語音軟體：Ｄｉｓｃｏｒｄ<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.warcraftlogs.com/guild/calendar/361909/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.warcraftlogs.com%2Fguild%2Fcalendar%2F361909%2F&d=Hc1%2BdZ9%2BT6jd8PNkX1crpk%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=150e47e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.warcraftlogs.com/guild/calendar/361909/</a><br />\n聯絡方式:honglai321#3610 Or Kelami#3527"},{"pid":"9bc17a8ced559727f81b5e2baa14a7e93c338ece","tid":894482,"uid":44727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T12:44:46.000Z","msg":"DH係雞係公廁"},{"pid":"80f387761beab727667609a0e3aa4d19e8e5bcf9","tid":894482,"uid":108226,"lik